{
  "texts": [
    "Abbreviations EMB: Theory of embedded cognition.",
    "; EXT: Theory of extended cognition.",
    "; TET: Technology-Education Tension; LLM: Large Language Model",
    "This tool may prove beneficial by offering 1) efficient and time-saving creation of learning assessments(Zhai",
    "2022; 2023; Baidoo-Anu and Owusu Ansah, 2023); 2) enhancement of pedagogical practices by assisting teachers' production of quizzes, exams, syllabuses, and lesson plans (Rudolf 2023; Atlas 2023); 3) easily available personalized tutoring and feedback for students (Mhlanga 2023); 4) creation of outlines for organizing ideas (Kasneci et al., 2023) and 5) facilitation of brainstorming."
  ]
}